{"tid":1119377,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IT碩士脫節，人工不及IVE生，建築工程收入最高","createTime":"2019-04-22T00:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T11:06:19.000Z","uid":162866,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cf960d39b4914a1306664c20cf725abe5d0a71","tid":1119377,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T00:48:56.000Z","msg":"【大公報訊】記者朱樂怡報道：香港創科起步遲，令IT界薪金與學歷不成正比。有調查發現，從事資訊科技（IT）的學士畢業生，起薪點較碩士生還要高4%。有業界人士表示，IT碩士仍沿用十年前訂下的課程，側重理論，不符合業界着重技術的要求，而科技世界變化急促，&ldquo;（碩士生）讀了六年，已經脱離現實，IVE畢業生如果有實戰經驗，人工會較高。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　香港人才管理協會與浸會大學工商管理學院人力資源策略發展中心昨日公佈，今年七至九月以問卷調查11個行業、96間本港公司，涉及逾11.5萬名僱員。調查顯示，今年整體應屆學士畢業生的起薪點為14216元，較去年高3.3%；碩士或以上的應屆畢業生起薪點則較去年低6.8%，月入14316元。<br />\n<br />\n　　商界重經驗 不要象牙塔<br />\n<br />\n　　若按科目劃分，<span style=\"color: red;\">大學的建築畢業生起薪點最高，學士平均月薪17814元，碩士或以上為17852元；其次為工程，學士月薪14699元，碩士則有15117元，都是碩士畢業生薪金高過學士。不過，IT學士畢業生起薪點達14983元，碩士生反而只有14406元。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　香港互聯網專業協會副會長、智慧城市聯盟金融科技小組主席陳家豪回覆《大公報》記者查詢時稱，業界需要的是技術人員，&ldquo;一畢業出來，就要交到貨&rdquo;，但大學課程直至今年，才加入大數據分析、人工智能等業界需要的新技術，有實戰經驗的IVE畢業生變相更吃香，人工甚至會比大學生高，而碩士生在象牙塔，與時代脱節，更不是商界需要的人才。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2017/1020/3505077.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com.hk%2Fpaper%2Fq%2F2017%2F1020%2F3505077.html&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6mztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=4e889218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2017/1020/3505077.html</a>"},{"pid":"789878bf4dcb13181c439e99292678db8833930c","tid":1119377,"uid":146063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T00:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a60685d1efd0194411083346381c674db57afde","tid":1119377,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T00:59:52.000Z","msg":"繼續打飛機吹奏啦你個on9仔"},{"pid":"a2f93ca0e9032dabba3567047faa0b1efeea77fb","tid":1119377,"uid":109923,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"香港政府靠賣地維生，建築再衰都衰唔過IT"},{"pid":"785b009351c867e7b72b43137734eedfc98ca9cf","tid":1119377,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"IVE仔瘋狂打J<br />\n<br />\nIVE世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca9fa2bf9c9dcd81378fa03eb70bebf35d6dbe1","tid":1119377,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:07:40.000Z","msg":"其實加入禮儀廉人工先最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3241ecb43231d7aa2dd5be9b3e5ff5419b6ed2","tid":1119377,"uid":162866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a2f93ca0e9032dabba3567047faa0b1efeea77fb","tid":1119377,"uid":109923,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"香港政府靠賣地維生，建築再衰都衰唔過IT"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:32:25.000Z","msg":"香港政府仲識自己造地來賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁過印錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd1ba4b6b1e96fd98a755641d64783d19dc36d6","tid":1119377,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T02:00:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾大公報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93be9fc0a114fdcd1e5a2a9b3b355a88ca056608","tid":1119377,"uid":49690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T02:00:45.000Z","msg":"IT打手: IT前途好好 做2,3年就4,50K以上 每日準時收工多假期 好舒服無壓力 希望多啲年青人入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a203353ac46124467d6bbd92c998eb78320219ef","tid":1119377,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-